	<div class="commentBody">
		<div id="comment_body_64319885"><p><div class="quote"><p>to ask those in the EU what they pay for car insurance for a similar or same car.</p></div><p>Many people insure a new car and then keep the policy at the same level as the car ages and dramatically declines in value, while the insurance company happily charges them high premiums to over-insure their vehicle.</p><p>Other people shop around every year before renewing.</p><p>So, it's common for people with the same car and similar driving records to pay very different rates.</p></div>
	</div>

