		</div>
	</div>
	<div class="commentBody">
		<div id="comment_body_64320077"><p>If you're buying new... tell the salesman you want to see the car function with the DCM disabled before you sign.  If you're buying used, it should be easy enough to test.</p><p>This assumes that the answer can't be had with some Internet searching.</p><p>Then comes the difficult part - if you're really dedicated to your privacy and principles... you have to walk away from any car that spies on you and can't be stopped from doing so.</p></div>
